i just stopped babysitting for extra money and I'm not sure we can swing that kind-of trip, I know we would all love it, my dh would want to go with too, its just if I can save the money now or not,
I'm in this stupid big expensive house now, I know, poor me, but it still takes money to make the payments, can sell it some time here,

Anyway, I want to research it all and find out how much it would all take,

We'll see...
Thanks,
Kelli
